<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="ja"><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
	
	<meta http-equiv="Content-Language" content="ja">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=480">
	<title>美容室「Milk tea」</title>
	<meta name="title" content="美容室「Milk tea」">
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/stylesheets/assets/milktea-new/style.css">
	<link rel ="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.1.1/css/all.min.css">
	<script src="/images/assets/milk-tea-new/jquery-3.3.1.js"></script>
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="style.css">
</head>
<body id="page-index"><div id="bgLayer">
<div id="pagetop"></div>

	<header>
		<%= render :partial=>"#{LayoutScheme.asset_root}/milk-tea-new/header" %>
	</header>

	<main>
		<section>
				<div id="profile">
					<div class="profile-in all-center-1280 sp-LR15">
						<div class="wrapper-waku">
							<div class="cover-waku">
								<div class="contents-flex">
									<div class="left">
										<% 
											photo = '//placehold.it/327x327&amp;text=No Photo'
											unless @seed.photos.blank?
												photo = reorder_by_position_photo(@seed.photos, true).first
											end
										%>
										<div class="img-cover"><%= image_tag photo.clip.url(:panel) %><img src="/images/assets/milk-tea-new/horii.jpg" alt="堀井淳太"></div>
									</div>
									<div class="right">
										<div class="profile-text">
											<div class="profile-flex">
												<div class="name-flex">
													<div class="name"><%= @seed.name %></div>
													<div class="official-position-cover">
														<div class="official-position"><%= @seed.job_title %></div>
													</div>
												</div>
												<div class="insta-reserve-cover">
													<div class="insta-reserve">
														<div class="icon pointer1">
															<% unless @seed.social_facebook_uri.blank? %>
																<a href="<%= @seed.social_facebook_uri%>" target='_blank'><i class='fa-brands fa-facebook fa-2x'></i></a></a>
															<% end %>
															<% unless @seed.social_twitter_uri.blank? %>
																<a href="<%= @seed.social_twitter_uri %>" target='_blank'><i class='fa-brands fa-twitter fa-2x'></i></a>
															<% end %>
															<% unless @seed.social_instagram_uri.blank? %>
																<a href="<%= @seed.social_instagram_uri %>" target='_blank'><i class='fa-brands fa-instagram fa-2x'></i></a>
															<% end %>
															<% unless @seed.social_line_uri.blank? %>
																<a href="<%= @seed.social_line_uri %>" target='_blank'><i class='fa-brands fa-line fa-2x'></i></a>
															<% end %>
															<% unless @seed.social_pinterest_uri.blank? %>
																<a href="<%= @seed.social_pinterest_uri %>" target='_blank'><i class='fa-brands fa-pinterest fa-2x'></i></a>
															<% end %>
															<% unless @seed.social_tumblr_uri.blank? %>
																<a href="<%= @seed.social_tumblr_uri %>" target='_blank'><i class='fa-brands fa-tumblr fa-2x'></i></a>
															<% end %>
															<% unless @seed.web_reservation_uri.blank? %>
																<a href="<%= @staff.web_reservation_uri %>" target='_blank'><%= reservation_icon('WEB予約', 'fa-2x') %></a>
															<% end %>
																<%= hotpepper_staff_banner(@seed, false, 'vertical-align: top; padding-top: 1px;') %>
																<%= youtube_staff_banner(@seed, false) %>
															<a href="https://www.instagram.com/milkteagroup/"><img src="/images/assets/milk-tea-new/insta_icon.png" alt="インスタグラム　アイコン"></a>
														</div>
														<div class="hotpepper-cover">
															<a href="https://beauty.hotpepper.jp/slnH000230521/coupon/">
																<div class="hotpepper pointer1">
																	<div class="hot-logo-cover">
																		<img src="/images/assets/milk-tea-new/hpb_icon_bk.png" alt="ホットペッパー　ロゴ">
																	</div>
																		<div class="hotpepper-text">指名して予約する</div>
																</div>
															</a>
														</div>
													</div>
												</div>
											</div>
											<div class="charactor-cover">
												<div class="charactor">
													<div class="charactor-text">
														<% unless @seed.description.blank? %>
															<%= raw @seed.description %>
														<% end %>
													</div>
													<div class="charactor-text">好き：ラーメン、フットサル、釣り、温泉、お酒</div>
													<div class="charactor-text">嫌い：牡蠣、レバー、粕汁</div>
													<div class="charactor-text">休日：映画を観たり♪　雑貨や巡りしたり♪　<br class="no-display-pc">美味しいラーメン屋を探す旅</div>
													<div class="charactor-text">タイプ：ポジティブな人☆</div>
													<div class="charactor-text">受賞歴：</div>
													<div class="charactor-text"><span class="bold">2005</span> 年 <span class="bold">WD</span> 部門新潟大会　<span class="bold">3</span> 位</div>
													<div class="charactor-text"><span class="bold">2007</span> 年 <span class="bold">FE</span> 部門タチカワ　優秀賞</div>
													<div class="charactor-text"><span class="bold">2009</span> 年 <span class="bold">FE</span> EARTH 杯　準優勝</div>
													<div class="charactor-text"><span class="bold">2010</span> 年 <span class="bold">FE</span> EARTH 大会　<span class="bold">3</span> 位</div>
													<div class="charactor-text"><span class="bold">2011</span> 年 <span class="bold">FE</span> EARTH 大会　金賞</div>
													<div class="charactor-text"><span class="bold">2012</span> 年 <span class="bold">MO</span> 部門タチカワ　優秀賞　</div>
													<div class="charactor-text"><span class="bold">2015</span> 年 <span class="bold">THA</span> 新潟大会　優勝</div>
													<div class="charactor-text"><span class="bold">2016</span> 年 <span class="bold">THA</span> 新潟大会 3 位<span class="bold">3</span> 位</div>
													<div class="charactor-text">メッセージ：髪の悩みに合わせてアドバイスしながら、一緒に可愛いスタイル見つけましょ♪おまかせください (^^)</div>
												</div>
											</div>
										</div>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class="back-cover">
									<div class="back">
										<div class="text-cover-abso">
											<a href="<%= url_for :action=>'home', :anchor=>'stylist-jump', :wkey=>@website.wsite_hash_key %>">
												<div class="detail-arrow pointer3"> 
													<div></div>
													<div class="detail">戻る</div>
													<div class="arrow">→</div>
												</div>
											</a>
										</div>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
	</main>

	<footer>
		<div id="inquiry">
			<div class="wrapper-waku">
				<div class="cover-waku">
					<div id="footer-under">
						<div class="wrapper-mini">
							<div class="cover-mini">
								<div class="contents-mini">c 2022 Milk tea LLC All rights Reserved.</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>	
		</div>
	</footer>
	<div id="return-cover">
		<a href="#pagetop" class="return">&#8743;</a>
	</div>

</div>
</body></html>
